()🔥 Event kya hota hai?
👉 Event = “kuch hua system me”
Aur uske baad → rule / workflow / task trigger hota hai.
👉 Event = system ka heartbeat ❤️
Har choti-badi cheez ek event hai — aur har event kisi action ko trigger karta hai
❌ SailPoint me “Event” koi direct class nahi hoti
👉 Matlab:-
Event naam ki koi standard class (jaise Task, WorkflowCase, ApprovalSet) SailPoint API me nahi hoti
Ye ek concept (trigger/occurrence) hai.

⚙️ Event ka use kaha hota hai?
Rule trigger karne me
Workflow start karne me
Notification bhejne me
Provisioning execute karne me

🎯 Common Events in SailPoint:-
1️⃣ Identity Events:-
Identity create hua
Identity update hua
Identity delete hua

👉 Example:-
User create hua → Event trigger → Provisioning start

2️⃣ Provisioning Events:-
Account create / update / delete
Entitlement assign / remove

👉 Example:-
Role assign hua → Event → AD account create

3️⃣ Certification Events:-
Access review start
Approval / rejection

👉 Example:-
Manager ne reject kiya → Event → access remove

4️⃣ Workflow Events;-
Workflow start / complete
Approval step trigger

5️⃣ Policy Events:-
Policy violation detect hua
👉 Example:-
User ke paas 2 conflicting roles → Event → violation alert

6️⃣ Account Lifecycle Events:-
Account Enable
Account Disable
Account Lock / Unlock
Password Reset
👉 Example:-
User ka account disable hua → Event → access revoke

7️⃣ Role / Entitlement Events:-
Role Assigned
Role Removed
Entitlement Granted
Entitlement Revoked
👉 Example:-
Role assign → Event → provisioning start

8️⃣ Aggregation Events:-
Account Aggregation Start
Account Aggregation Complete
Identity Refresh
👉 Example:-
HR system se data aaya → Event → identities update

9️⃣ Task Events:-
Task Start
Task Complete
Task Failed
👉 Example:-
Certification task complete → Event → report generate

🔟 Approval Events:-
Approval Requested
Approval Approved
Approval Rejected
Approval Escalated
👉 Example:-
Manager ne approve kiya → Event → next step

1️⃣1️⃣ WorkItem Events:-
WorkItem Created
WorkItem Assigned
WorkItem Completed
WorkItem Expired
👉 Example:-
Approval workitem create hua → Event → email notification

1️⃣2️⃣ Audit Events:-
