-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
🚀 1️⃣ Identity Events (Object = Identity):
Event	               Condition	       Method (kis object ka)
Identity Created----identity.isNew()-----------Identity
Identity Updated----identity.isModified()------Identity
Identity Deleted----identity.isDeleted()-------Identity
Attribute Changed---!oldVal.equals(newVal)-----Identity (getAttribute())
Manager Changed-----!oldMgr.equals(newMgr)-----Identity
Role Assigned-------identity.getAssignedRoles()compare-----Identity
Role Removed--------old vs new roles compare---------------Identity

🚀 2️⃣ Account / Provisioning Events (Object = AccountRequest / AttributeRequest)
Event	                  Condition	                          Method (kis object ka)
Account Created	    accReq.getOperation().equals("Create")	     AccountRequest
Account Updated	    accReq.getOperation().equals("Modify")	     AccountRequest
Account Deleted	    accReq.getOperation().equals("Delete")	     AccountRequest
Entitlement Added	attrReq.getOperation().equals("Add")	     AttributeRequest
Entitlement Removed	attrReq.getOperation().equals("Remove")      AttributeRequest

🚀 3️⃣ Approval Events (Object = ApprovalSet / WorkItem)
Event	               Condition	                  Method (kis object ka)
Approval Pending	set.isPending()	                        ApprovalSet
Approval Approved	set.isApproved()	                     ApprovalSet
Approval Rejected	set.isRejected()	                     ApprovalSet
WorkItem Created	workItem.getState().equals("Pending")	WorkItem
WorkItem Completed	workItem.getState().equals("Completed")  WorkItem

🚀 4️⃣ Task / Job Events (Object = TaskResult):-
Event	              Condition	                         Method (kis object ka)
Task Started	taskResult.getStatus().equals("Running")	TaskResult
Task Completed	taskResult.getStatus().equals("Completed")	TaskResult
Task Failed	    taskResult.getStatus().equals("Failed")	    TaskResult

🚀 5️⃣ Workflow Events (Object = WorkflowCase):-
Event	                  Condition	                    Method (kis object ka)
Workflow Started	wfCase.getState().equals("Running")	    WorkflowCase
Workflow Completed	wfCase.getState().equals("Completed")	WorkflowCase
Workflow Rejected	wfCase.getState().equals("Rejected")	WorkflowCase

🚀 6️⃣ Certification Events (Object = Certification / CertificationItem):-
Event	                     Condition	                    Method (kis object ka)
Certification Started	  cert.getPhase().equals("Active")	   Certification
Certification Completed   cert.isComplete()	                   Certification
Access Approved	          item.isApproved()                    CertificationItem
Access Revoked	          item.isRevoked()	                   CertificationItem

🚀 7️⃣ Policy / Violation Events (Object = PolicyViolation):-
Event	                   Condition	           Method (kis object ka)
Violation Created	    violation != null	        PolicyViolation
Violation Mitigated	    violation.isMitigated()	    PolicyViolation

🚀 8️⃣ WorkItem / Escalation Events (Object = WorkItem):-
Event	                      Condition	                 Method (kis object ka)
WorkItem Escalated	workItem.getEscalationLevel() > 0	      WorkItem
Reminder Triggered	currentDate.after(reminderDate)	          WorkItem

🚀 9️⃣ Aggregation / Refresh Events (Object = TaskResult / Identity):-
Event	                      Condition	                            Method (kis object ka)
Aggregation Completed	taskResult.getStatus().equals("Completed")	   TaskResult
Identity Refreshed	    identity.isModified()	                       Identity

🚀 🔟 Access Request Events (Object = AccessRequest / ApprovalItem)
Event	                           Condition	                        Method (kis object ka)
Access Request Submitted	    request.getState().equals("Submitted")	    AccessRequest
Access Request Approved	        item.isApproved()	                        ApprovalItem
Access Request Rejected	        item.isRejected()	                        ApprovalItem
Access Request Cancelled	    request.getState().equals("Cancelled")	    AccessRequest

🚀 1️⃣1️⃣ Role / Entitlement Events (Object = Identity / RoleAssignment)
Event	                        Condition	                        Method (kis object ka)
Role Assigned	        identity.getAssignedRoles().contains(role)	Identity
Role Removed	        !identity.getAssignedRoles().contains(role)	Identity
Entitlement Granted	     identity.getEntitlements().contains(ent)	Identity
Entitlement Revoked	     !identity.getEntitlements().contains(ent)	Identity

🚀 1️⃣2️⃣ Password / Account Security Events (Object = Identity / Link)
Event	                    Condition	                 Method (kis object ka)
Password Changed	identity.getPasswordLastSet() != null	Identity
Password Expired	identity.isPasswordExpired()	        Identity
Account Locked	     link.isLocked()	                     Link
Account Unlocked	 !link.isLocked()	                     Link

🚀 1️⃣3️⃣ Connector / Integration Events (Object = Application / ConnectorResult)
Event	                Condition	          Method (kis object ka)
Connection Success	 result.isSuccess()	        ConnectorResult
Connection Failed	 !result.isSuccess()	    ConnectorResult
Provisioning Sent	 plan != null	            ProvisioningPlan
Provisioning Failed	 result.getErrors()!= null	ConnectorResult

🚀 1️⃣4️⃣ Audit / Logging Events (Object = AuditEvent):-
Event	             Condition	                          Method (kis object ka)
Login Success	audit.getAction().equals("loginSuccess")	AuditEvent
Login Failed	audit.getAction().equals("loginFailed")	    AuditEvent
Access Changed	audit.getAction().equals("accessChange")	AuditEvent

🚀 1️⃣5️⃣ Delegation Events (Object = WorkItem):-
Event	                   Condition	                            Method (kis object ka)
Approval Delegated	workItem.getDelegatedTo() != null	                WorkItem
Delegation Expired	currentDate.after(workItem.getDelegationExpiry())	WorkItem

🚀 1️⃣6️⃣ Escalation Events (Object = WorkItem):-
Event	                         Condition	               Method (kis object ka)
Escalation Triggered	workItem.getEscalationLevel() > 0	WorkItem
Escalation Increased	level > oldLevel	                WorkItem

🚀 1️⃣7️⃣ Scheduler / Job Events (Object = TaskSchedule / TaskResult):-
Event	                Condition	                Method (kis object ka)
Job Scheduled	      schedule != null	                TaskSchedule
Job Triggered	      taskResult.getLaunched() != null	TaskResult
Job Missed	          currentTime.after(scheduleTime)	TaskSchedule

🚀 1️⃣8️⃣ Data Change Events (Object = Identity):-
Event	                  Condition	              Method (kis object ka)
Email Changed	    !oldEmail.equals(newEmail)	      Identity
Department Changed	!oldDept.equals(newDept)	      Identity
Location Changed	!oldLoc.equals(newLoc)	          Identity

🚀 1️⃣9️⃣ Risk / Compliance Events (Object = Identity / RiskScore):-
Event	                        Condition	                   Method (kis object ka)
High Risk Detected	           risk.getScore() > threshold	          RiskScore
Risk Increased	               newScore > oldScore	                  RiskScore

🚀 2️⃣0️⃣ System / Performance Events (Object = SystemMonitor):-
Event	        Condition	                   Method (kis object ka)
High Load	system.getLoad() > limit	          SystemMonitor
Memory High	system.getMemoryUsage() > limit	      SystemMonitor

